===Home media===
''Fruitvale Station'' was available in Digital HD via [[Anchor Bay Entertainment|Anchor Bay]] on December 31, 2013.<ref>{{cite web|last=McNary|first=Dave|title=<U+2018>Lee Daniels<U+2019> The Butler<U+2019> Returns to Theaters; <U+2018>Fruitvale Station<U+2019> Gets Early Digital Release|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/lee-daniels-the-butler-returning-to-u-s-theaters-1200918517/|work=Variety|accessdate=December 5, 2013|date=December 4, 2013}}</ref> [[DVD]] and [[Blu-ray disc|Blu-ray Disc]] releases are scheduled for January 14, 2014.<ref>{{cite web|last=Obenson|first=Tambay A.|title=TWC Announces 1/14 DVD, Blu-Ray Combo Pack & VOD Release Of 'Fruitvale Station' (Details)|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/twc-announces-january-2014-dvd-blu-ray-combo-pack-vod-release-of-fruitvale-station-details|work=[[IndieWire]]|accessdate=November 21, 2013|date=November 20, 2013}}</ref>

